          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/vitanuova/" class=" " title="Adiyat">Adiyat</a>
                (Spiritual Chivalry Style)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="36399277">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">不出所料，阿喀琉斯在秩序的并叙中尽情发挥，这才能让他的愤怒保持在一个巧妙的、英雄般的沸点上。

Achilles, as can be expected, makes the most of the parallel in order to keep his wrath at a fine, heroic boiling point.

in order to是“为了……”而不是“在秩序中”，&quot;在秩序中&quot;应该是in the order。“阿喀琉斯尽可能地利用了【阿伽门农抢走布里塞伊斯和帕里斯抢走海伦这两件事】这种平行关系（或类比..</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2015-10-22 10:10</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>不出所料，阿喀琉斯在秩序的并叙中尽情发挥，这才能让他的愤怒保持在一个巧妙的、英雄般的沸点上。</q></blockquote><div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>Achilles, as can be expected, makes the most of the parallel in order to keep his wrath at a fine, heroic boiling point.<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>in order to是“为了……”而不是“在秩序中”，&quot;在秩序中&quot;应该是in the order。“阿喀琉斯尽可能地利用了【阿伽门农抢走布里塞伊斯和帕里斯抢走海伦这两件事】这种平行关系（或类比）”
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
</span>
