          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/36399129/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/36399129/" class="">第158页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/vitanuova/" class=" " title="Adiyat">Adiyat</a>
                (Spiritual Chivalry Style)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="36399129">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">他沉湎于这些明哲保身的想法之中，烧杀枪掠、争强好胜（在其他方面也许很带劲）都无法让一个人回心（psyche）转意，一旦他已经吃了秤砣铁了心。 


...and he indulges in such sound but unheroic reflections that no plundering and prize winning (pleasant as it may be in other respects) will bring back the psyche of a man once it has passed the barrier of his teeth. 

典型的荷马表达，直译为“一旦灵魂（psy...</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2015-10-22 09:50</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>他沉湎于这些明哲保身的想法之中，烧杀枪掠、争强好胜（在其他方面也许很带劲）都无法让一个人回心（psyche）转意，一旦他已经吃了秤砣铁了心。</q></blockquote> <div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>...and he indulges in such sound but unheroic reflections that no plundering and prize winning (pleasant as it may be in other respects) will bring back the psyche of a man once it has passed the barrier of his teeth. <div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>典型的荷马表达，直译为“一旦灵魂（psyche）从齿篱溜了出去就再也回不来了”，即不能死而复生的意思，不是吃了秤砣铁了心。 

